---
title: SuperQuick Moroccan Chicken Stew with Lemony Couscous
description: Need dinner fast? This super-quick stew is coming to your rescue! Tender chicken pieces, Moroccan-inspired spices, spinach and veggies come together in a delicious meal that will instantly warm you up from the inside out.

